Public Remarks: A gardener's delight! This charming 4 bed/2 bath single-story home is perfectly placed in the middle of the quiet Papago Manor Subdivision. With close proximity to ASU, The Phoenix Zoo, Desert Botanical Gardens, Tempe Town Lake and Tempe Marketplace, you'll have a variety of trendy shopping, delicious restaurants, and unique culture at your fingertips!  Pride of ownership is evident in this home and new owners should delight in this

Public Remarks: Heart of Tempe! Beautifully updated 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home near ASU and the 60 is the perfect new place for you to call home. The spacious backyard is a fantastic space to host get-togethers! And don't skip over the pool! Just what is needed when summer shows it's sunny face! Truly a space that can fit a multitude of buyers including those looking to buy their first home close to all that Mill has to offer, parents looking to provide a home for their new ASU students, or even a first rental property with the promise of consistent renters near the university. Public Remarks: Beautifully remodeled Tempe home with a pool, on a corner lot of a desirable cul-de-sac street! It offers 4 beds, 2 baths, a 2-car garage and a low-maintenance front yard. Upgraded flooring throughout, including gorgeous wood plank in main areas and carpet in the bedrooms. Stunning kitchen opens out and comes complete with white shaker cabinetry, quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar opening out to a cozy nook. Fireplace in the family room, with convenient back patio access. Ceiling fans in the family and living rooms. Main bedroom features a remodeled bath with dual sinks, tiled walk-in shower, and spacious closet. Oversized backyard includes a storage shed, a large covered patio, abundant grass and mature trees. This one won't last!

Public Remarks: LOVED and IMMACULATELY MAINTAINED! As you drive up, notice by the innate curb appeal enticing you to see more!  Step inside to enjoy the cheery bright ambiance. The living/dining rooms are perfect for enjoying your large screen TV or a game room. The kitchen is open to the large family room having loads of windows allowing you to enjoy the scenery of the glistening pool. The kitchen boasts stainless appliances & quartz counters. The other three bedrooms are also roomy and share the hall bath with an updated vanity. Outside is a nice covered patio, plenty of deck for entertaining & an enticing pool. (Please click more)

Public Remarks: Beautiful 4 bed, 2 bath property with manicured landscape is now on the market! Inside, you will find a perfectly flowing layout showcasing soothing palette, tile floors, fresh paint & an inviting living area. The remodeled kitchen offers a plethora of white cabinets with crown moulding, stylish backsplash, granite counters, & a two tone center island with a breakfast bar. Two remodeled bathrooms with tiled showers. Master bedroom featuring a private bathroom with designer's tile shower & a well-sized closet. Spacious AZ room is ideal for relaxing without worrying about the weather. Host fun gatherings in the fabulous backyard surrounded by fruit trees, green grass, a storage shed, & endless blue skies! Minutes from restaurants, hiking trails, & the Phoenix Zoo!

You'll definitely enjoy the primary bedroom offering patio access, walk-in closet, & private bathroom. This backyard has a covered patio & fenced-in pool great for those hot summer days! Dreams do come true! Make this beauty yours before it's gone!

Public Remarks: Beautiful updated home in the heart of the desirable Tempe Lakes neighborhood. Fully remodeled from top to bottom and offers curb appeal for days. Natural light, greenery and bold design join forces to create this stunning oasis in the desert. This paradise features 4 bedrooms, 2 and 1/2 baths, a 2 car garage, a large backyard/patio saturated with lush greenery, a large grapefruit tree, cactus garden, skylights throughout and newer A/C unit/ Water heater for ultimate comfort.     The Lakes neighborhood features the lake, fishing, boating and the clubhouse with Olympic heated pool, spa, tennis and indoor racquetball courts, fitness center and more!
